content: This is a great app, really well put together and easy to use. I only have one question, is there any way to input a custom race?
Yet another amazing builder app for Paizo systems! Would love to see a Starship builder, and vehicle's as a future option!
Excellent app, especially considering the amount of information it's handling. Support for the app is equally excellent, well worth the purchase price.

Fairly intuitive, but I don't like the only option for leveling up, being to set your level. It be nice if you could give yourself enough ex to level up. Then it helps to show you what you've unlocked. Very nice starting point app though.

It seems like a nice app, but i quickly had to discard it as it has no room for customization. For example: i wanted to use a race that are not among the ones that are in the core rulebook, therefore it wasn't available in the app and i also had no way to add it. I do like the app, and if you make room for customization, i would love to use it instead of the pdf :)

Incredibly intuitive. Contains content from every book, as far as i can tell. Worth spending money on. One thing that would improve it would be the ability to add 3rd party or custom content if you wanted. Overall, very happy with Starbuilder.

Thank you so much for this. Been waiting for an app like this for a long while. Well worth the money, i highly recommend buying this app and supporting the creator. Again, thanks for making this. Look forward to what is to come. Keep up the great work.
Great app, wish you could read the details of items you have in your inventory. Doesn't stop me from recommending it to people.
An amazing character creator for Starfinder. Makes character creation and character management very easy.
